iO , or iO Chicago , -LRB- formerly known as `` ImprovOlympic '' -RRB- is an improv theater and training center in central Chicago , with a branch in Los Angeles called iO West .
The theater both teaches and hosts performances of improvisational comedy .
It was founded in 1981 by the late Del Close and Charna Halpern .
The theater has many notable alumni , including Amy Poehler and Stephen Colbert .